msgid "# Tutorial"
msgstr "# チュートリアル"

msgid ""
"This document describes how to use Groonga-HTTP step by step.\n"
"If you don't install Groonga-HTTP yet, [install][install] Groonga-HTTP before "
"you read this document."
msgstr ""
"このドキュメントは、Groonga-HTTPの使い方を段階的に説明しています。まだ、Groonga-HTTPをインストールしていない場合は、このドキュメント"
"を読む前にGroonga-HTTPをインストールしてください。"

msgid "## Drilldown {#drilldown}"
msgstr "## ドリルダウン {#drilldown}"

msgid ""
"drilldown enables us to get the number of records which belongs to specific th"
"e value of column at once."
msgstr ""
"drilldown はカラムの値ごとにレコード数を数える機能を提供します。値ごとに別々のクエリーになるのではなく、1回のクエリーですべての値に対してレコード"
"数を数えます。"

msgid "Example:"
msgstr "例:"

msgid ""
"```perl\n"
"use Groonga::HTTP;"
msgstr ""

msgid "my $groonga = Groonga::HTTP->new;"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"my @result = $groonga->select(\n"
"   table => 'Entries',\n"
"   output_columns => '_key,tag',\n"
"   drilldown => 'tag'\n"
");"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"#Result\n"
"#[\n"
"#  [\n"
"#    \"Hello\",\n"
"#    1\n"
"#  ],\n"
"#  [\n"
"#    \"Groonga\",\n"
"#    2\n"
"#  ],\n"
"#  [\n"
"#    \"Senna\",\n"
"#    2\n"
"#  ]\n"
"#]\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid "The above example shows the following."
msgstr "上記の例は以下のことを示しています。"

msgid ""
"  * The number of records that the value of ``tag`` is \"Hello\" is 1.\n"
"  * The number of records that the value of ``tag`` is \"Groonga\" is 2.\n"
"  * The number of records that the value of ``tag`` is \"Senna\" is 2."
msgstr ""
"  * ``tag`` の値が \"Hello\" であるレコードの数は1。\n"
"  * ``tag`` の値が \"Groonga\" であるレコードの数は2。\n"
"  * ``tag`` の値が \"Senna\" であるレコードの数は2。"

msgid "## Filter of the result of drilldown {#drilldown-filter}"
msgstr "## ドリルダウン結果のフィルター {#drilldown-filter}"

msgid ""
"We can filter the result of drilldown by ``drilldown_filter``.\n"
"We specify the filter condition against the drilled down result into ``drilldo"
"wn_filter``."
msgstr ""
"``drilldown_filter`` を使ってドリルダウン結果をフィルターできます。\n"
"``drilldown_filter`` にドリルダウン結果に対するフィルター条件を指定します。"

msgid "Here is an example to suppress tags that are occurred only once."
msgstr "以下は1回しか出現していないタグを除く例です。"

msgid ""
"my @result = $groonga->select(\n"
"   table => 'Entries',\n"
"   output_columns => '_key,tag',\n"
"   drilldown => 'tag',\n"
"   drilldown_filter => '_nsubrecs > 1'\n"
");"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"#Result\n"
"#[\n"
"#  [\n"
"#    \"Groonga\",\n"
"#    2\n"
"#  ],\n"
"#  [\n"
"#    \"Senna\",\n"
"#    2\n"
"#  ]\n"
"#]\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

msgid "## Sort of result {#sort-of-result}"
msgstr "## 結果のソート {#sort-of-result}"

msgid ""
"Groonga-HTTP can sort search results by a specific value of a column.\n"
"The default of the order is ascending order.\n"
"We can reverse the order by the prefix of \"-\"."
msgstr ""
"Groonga-HTTPは、検索結果を特定のカラムの値でソートできます。デフォルトの順序は昇順です。\n"
"\"-\"接頭辞によって、順序を逆にできます。"

msgid "# Ascending order"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"my @result = $groonga->select(\n"
"  table => 'Site',\n"
"  columns => 'title',\n"
"  query => 'six OR seven',\n"
"  output_columns => '_id, title',\n"
"  sort_keys => 'id'\n"
");"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"# Result\n"
"#    [\n"
"#      [\n"
"#        6,\n"
"#        'test test test test record six.'\n"
"#      ],\n"
"#      [\n"
"#        7,\n"
"#        'test test test record seven.'\n"
"#      ],\n"
"#    ],"
msgstr ""

msgid "# Descending order"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"my @result = $groonga->select(\n"
"  table => 'Site',\n"
"  columns => 'title',\n"
"  query => 'six OR seven',\n"
"  output_columns => '_id, title',\n"
"  sort_keys => '-id'\n"
");"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"# Result\n"
"#    [\n"
"#      [\n"
"#        7,\n"
"#        'test test test record seven.'\n"
"#      ],\n"
"#      [\n"
"#        6,\n"
"#        'test test test test record six.'\n"
"#      ],\n"
"#    ],"
msgstr ""

msgid "```"
msgstr ""

msgid "## Set weight to the column"
msgstr "## カラムに重みを設定する"

msgid ""
"Groonga-HTTP can set the weight to a column.\n"
"We adjust the value of score by this feature."
msgstr ""
"Groonga-HTTPはカラムに重みを設定できます。\n"
"この機能によってスコアーの値を調整できます。"

msgid ""
"For example, the weight of the content column is twice in the following exampl"
"e.\n"
"This weight allocation means content column value is more important rather tha"
"n _key column value."
msgstr ""
"例えば、以下の例では、 content カラムの重みを2倍しています。\n"
"これは、 _key カラムの値より content カラムの値のほうが重要だという意味になります。"

msgid ""
"```\n"
"my @result = $groonga->select(\n"
"   table => 'Entries',\n"
"   match_columns => '_key || content * 2',\n"
"   query => 'groonga',\n"
"   output_columns => '_key,content,_score'\n"
");"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"# Result\n"
"# [\n"
"#   [\n"
"#     \"Groonga\",\n"
"#     \"I started to use Groonga. It's very fast!\",\n"
"#     3,\n"
"#   ]\n"
"# ],\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

